text: Did you know that Woodbury County and our region have higher rates of sexually transmitted infections? 🤦‍♀️ The Siouxland District Health Department is working to change that! 💪 They offer free treatment plans for those diagnosed and free condoms in the lobby restrooms. 💕 Let's work together to reduce the incidence of STIs in our community! 🚫💔 Follow the link to make an appointment and talk to a medical professional. 👉🏼
